 《Wicked》同唱原声带在流媒体平台上发布https://www.nme.com/news/music/wicked-sing-along-soundtrack-released-on-streaming-platforms-3824072?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wicked-sing-along-soundtrack-released-on-流媒体平台Daniel PetersFri, 20 Dec 2024 14:40:29 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824072 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="辛西娅·埃里沃在《魔法坏女巫》中饰演艾尔法芭。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张专辑在圣诞节电影“跟唱”重新发行之前到达</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wicked-sing-along-soundtrack-released-on-streaming-platforms-3824072">在流媒体平台上发布的《Wicked》后跟唱原声带</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="辛西娅·埃里沃在《魔法坏女巫》中饰演艾尔法芭。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Wicked-fim-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>Wicked</em></a>原声带的跟唱版本已在流媒体平台上发布 - 聆听（或跟唱）下面的专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wicked-movie-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-3814095">《邪恶》评论：热门音乐剧将反重力的飞跃搬上大银幕</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Wicked: The Soundtrack (Sing-Along)》今天（12 月 20 日）由环球影业、Republic Records 和 Verve Records 发行。它收录了原专辑中的所有 11 首曲目，没有主唱，而最终的曲目则有管弦乐队的伴奏以及背景人声。</p><p>在一份新闻稿（来自<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/sing-along-version-wicked-soundtrack-released-1236091143/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道</em></a>》）中，声明中写道：“这是<em>《魔法坏女巫》</em>粉丝展示声乐肌肉并成为他们最喜欢的原声带主唱的绝佳机会。”</p><p> “跟唱配乐为奥兹国的所有公民提供了独特的能力，可以与电影的电影管弦乐队和背景歌手一起演唱他们最喜欢的邪恶歌曲。”播放下面的专辑。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：邪恶女巫：原声带（合唱）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/5ysbHCFYJ5UyCJ2zP6FGGd?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="邪恶女巫原声带合唱：挑战地心引力" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CDiT_SsL2wY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这张专辑在圣诞节（12 月 25 日）电影重新上映之前发布，这一次，观众通过显示为字幕的歌词来跟随音乐曲目一起唱歌。</p><p>这部由乔恩·M·朱 (Jon M Chu) 执导的电影由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a> 、辛西娅·埃里沃 (Cynthia Erivo)、乔纳森·贝利<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michelle-yeoh">(Jonathan Bailey)、杨紫琼 (Michelle Yeoh)</a> 、彼特·丁拉基 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peter-dinklage">Peter Dinklage) 和杰夫</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-goldblum">·高布伦 (Jeff Goldblum)</a>主演，于上个月上映，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wicked-will-be-uks-biggest-film-of-the-year-predicts-cinema-boss-3815044">专家预测为今年最卖座的电影</a>。</p><p>尽管这部音乐剧的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/glicked-fails-to-match-barbenheimer-at-box-office-but-still-ends-post-summer-slump-3815529">票房成绩未能与“巴本海默”现象相媲美</a>，但它仍然表现得非常好——据环球影业称，首映后在国内收获了 1.14 亿美元（9060 万英镑），在全球收获了 1.642 亿美元（1.305 亿英镑）。工作室估计。</p><p>公众对这部电影的热烈反响也导致影迷们穿着戏服前来观看放映—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wicked-fan-told-to-wipe-off-green-face-paint-before-entering-cinema-3816486">一名影迷在涂着绿色面漆出现时被电影院工作人员拒之门外</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3816900" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3816900" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3816900" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="阿丽亚娜·格兰德和辛西娅·埃里沃" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_wicked_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3816900" class="wp-caption-text">阿丽亚娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande) 和辛西娅·埃里沃 (Cynthia Erivo) 出席 2024 年 11 月 18 日在伦敦皇家节日音乐厅举行的《邪恶魔法：第一部分》欧洲首映式 图片来源：Karwai Tang/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wicked-first-screening-has-rave-reviews-what-a-fantastic-movie-the-ultimate-crowd-pleaser-of-2024-3814030">评论家们很快就赞扬了两位主角的声乐表演</a>，尼克·莱文在<em>《NME》</em>对<em>《邪恶女巫》</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/wicked-movie-ariana-grande-cynthia-erivo-3814095">四星评论</a>中指出，“埃里沃和格兰德的声音都非常出色”，并补充道，“至关重要的是，他们还拥有噼啪作响的化学反应，埃里沃的爆发力和格兰德巧妙的喜剧时机”。</p><p>这部电影的成功也引起了人们对格兰德音乐生涯的猜测——本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/no-plans-for-an-ariana-grande-tour-in-2025-label-says-3822784">她的唱片公司平息了这位歌手将在新年进行巡演的谣言</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ariana-grande-doesnt-see-herself-returning-to-music-anytime-soon-3823268">格兰德随后向<em>《综艺》</em>澄清了此事</a>：“我对表演感到非常感激，我认为我的粉丝知道音乐和舞台将永远是我生活的一部分，但我认为它不会很快发生。”</p><p> “我认为未来几年，希望我们能够探索不同的艺术形式，而且我认为表演现在感觉就像在家一样。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wicked-sing-along-soundtrack-released-on-streaming-platforms-3824072">在流媒体平台上发布的《Wicked》后跟唱原声带</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
