.nme.com/news/music/celeste-named-winner-of-brits-rising-star-award-2584545">全英音乐奖获奖者</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星</a>奖提名艺术家 2022 年单曲《To Love A Man》的后续作品。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/eddie-redmayne-confirms-his-return-for-the-day-of-the-jackal-season-two-3824058">埃迪·雷德梅尼 (Eddie Redmayne) 确认回归《豺狼之日》第二季的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
